{"type": "article", "id": 9604, "title": "Love Lamps 爱之灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-15T07:10:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235541IXH9qlZuCcf2QLUk.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>美国设计师 Sandro Lominashvili 推出的这款灯名为 “爱之灯”（Love Lamps），两盏灯相互独立而又彼此连结，象征着爱人之间缠绵的情意。两个灯均由透明塑料 3D 打印而成，通过不同的位置的变化，可以表现各种造型，营造不同的氛围。这款作品今年在米兰设计周进行了展出，这是<a href=\"http://www.sandrolominashvili.com/en/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family:arial, heltivitar, 'Hiragino Sans GB', STHeiti, 'Microsoft YaHei';\">设计师的个人主页</a>，敢兴趣的话可以点击查看更多作品。<br>\r\n</p>\n<div>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235539ipQPs09fAgNBbhlD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235540mXv0rskIDcOdBLuQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355409IWtHcTmns2LvGFP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235541poShmzQ7EI3xgbZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}